                            <comment id="12814213" author="jira-bugzilla-migration" created="Tue, 15 Oct 2013 10:24:59 -0400"  >&lt;p&gt;Darran Lofthouse &amp;lt;darran.lofthouse@redhat.com&amp;gt; made a comment on &lt;a href=&quot;https://bugzilla.redhat.com/show_bug.cgi?id=1019264&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow&quot;&gt;bug 1019264&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Proposing we make a change here as it is a tiny fix to address a usability issue.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;The real issue is that the end user is entering the wrong command and is not setting silent mode as they expect, however a couple of users have been caught by this so adding support for the approach users are using to set silent mode.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
